                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000d744a20e-37fd-4365-8afb-4c09f8a08e2b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001d744a20e-37fd-4365-8afb-4c09f8a08e2b">GLv‡b, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\left(a+b\right)=48…\left(i\right);\ \ \left(a-b\right)=10…(ii)\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000d744a20e-37fd-4365-8afb-4c09f8a08e2b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001d744a20e-37fd-4365-8afb-4c09f8a08e2b {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000006118ac68-4c96-4f65-ab67-bd1a1fcab6bb" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\left(i\right)+\left(ii\right)⇒a=29\ ,\ \left(i\right)-\left(ii\right)⇒b=19\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000016118ac68-4c96-4f65-ab67-bd1a1fcab6bb"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000006118ac68-4c96-4f65-ab67-bd1a1fcab6bb {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000016118ac68-4c96-4f65-ab67-bd1a1fcab6bb {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000bb33b065-a556-497f-a3b5-b044b169f22b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴a+2b=29+\left(19\times 2\right)=67\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001bb33b065-a556-497f-a3b5-b044b169f22b"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000bb33b065-a556-497f-a3b5-b044b169f22b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001bb33b065-a556-497f-a3b5-b044b169f22b {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0