                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000376c99d1-8918-4422-8882-41d63090f52e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∆=\left| \begin{matrix}a &amp; h &amp; g\\h &amp; b &amp; f\\g &amp; f &amp; c\\\end{matrix}\right| =\left| \begin{matrix}2 &amp; 2 &amp; 2\\2 &amp; 3 &amp; -1\\2 &amp; -1 &amp; 5\\\end{matrix}\right| =-12≠0\ ;\ \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001376c99d1-8918-4422-8882-41d63090f52e"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000376c99d1-8918-4422-8882-41d63090f52e {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001376c99d1-8918-4422-8882-41d63090f52e {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000175debbc-14b7-4ac7-a72d-e66dffefff26" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({h}^{2}={\left(\frac{4}{2}\right)}^{2}=4;\ ab=2.3=6\ ;{h}^{2}&lt;ab\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001175debbc-14b7-4ac7-a72d-e66dffefff26">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000175debbc-14b7-4ac7-a72d-e66dffefff26 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001175debbc-14b7-4ac7-a72d-e66dffefff26 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000007e710e87-0034-4d68-a59e-b610f5beb0e5" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017e710e87-0034-4d68-a59e-b610f5beb0e5"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000027e710e87-0034-4d68-a59e-b610f5beb0e5">mgxKiYwU Dce„&#203; </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000007e710e87-0034-4d68-a59e-b610f5beb0e5 {line-height: