                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000aa32e234-8b94-452e-8408-a6ed074945a1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(9\left({x}^{2}-2x\right)-16\left({y}^{2}+4y\right)=199\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001aa32e234-8b94-452e-8408-a6ed074945a1"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000aa32e234-8b94-452e-8408-a6ed074945a1 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001aa32e234-8b94-452e-8408-a6ed074945a1 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000004d45e00a-88f2-459a-837c-ad9c56cd545f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒9\left({x}^{2}-2x+1\right)-16\left({y}^{2}+4y+4\right)=199+9-64\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000014d45e00a-88f2-459a-837c-ad9c56cd545f"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000004d45e00a-88f2-459a-837c-ad9c56cd545f {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000014d45e00a-88f2-459a-837c-ad9c56cd545f {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000dc6ec0e1-110c-47af-8bf8-daf20f34ddac" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒9{\left(x-1\right)}^{2}-16{\left(y+2\right)}^{2}=144\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001dc6ec0e1-110c-47af-8bf8-daf20f34ddac"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000dc6ec0e1-110c-47af-8bf8-daf20f34ddac {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001dc6ec0e1-110c-47af-8bf8-daf20f34ddac {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000faf63733-fbd3-4197-9bab-a5ed5aa01d84" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒\frac{{\left(x-1\right)}^{2}}{{4}^{2}}-\frac{{\left(y+2\right)}^{2}}{{3}^{2}}=1\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001faf63733-fbd3-4197-9bab-a5ed5aa01d84"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000faf63733-fbd3-4197-9bab-a5ed5aa01d84 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001faf63733-fbd3-4197-9bab-a5ed5aa01d84 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000887c0c8e-dd65-49a4-b110-defcf0f18342" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001887c0c8e-dd65-49a4-b110-defcf0f18342">AmxgZU&#216;q: </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(y+2=±\frac{3}{4}\left(x-1\right)\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000887c0c8e-dd65-49a4-b110-defcf0f18342 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001887c0c8e-dd65-49a4-b110-defcf0f18342 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000018764ffb-80dd-4d09-9ccb-196758bbcf00" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000118764ffb-80dd-4d09-9ccb-196758bbcf00">Xv‡ji &#184;Ydj: </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{3}{4}\times \left(-\frac{3}{4}\right)=-\frac{9}{16}\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000018764ffb-80dd-4d09-9ccb-196758bbcf00 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000118764ffb-80dd-4d09-9ccb-196758bbcf00 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000002ecd201a-79a4-45b1-81d0-8d6a51933d