                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000dffcaa77-3547-4277-a465-e8d616d650ea" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(sin\ {θ+cos\ {θ=}}\frac{\sqrt{3}}{\sqrt{2}}⇒\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}sin\ {θ}+\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}cos\ {θ}=\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001dffcaa77-3547-4277-a465-e8d616d650ea"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000dffcaa77-3547-4277-a465-e8d616d650ea {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001dffcaa77-3547-4277-a465-e8d616d650ea {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000390e072e-79be-4f2a-8370-dd200f3bacca" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒cos\ {\frac{π}{4}}sin\ {θ}+sin\ {\frac{π}{4}}cos\ {θ}=\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001390e072e-79be-4f2a-8370-dd200f3bacca"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000390e072e-79be-4f2a-8370-dd200f3bacca {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001390e072e-79be-4f2a-8370-dd200f3bacca {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000ffa1f330-261c-477f-9bb9-2b1bf8de64d1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒sin\ {\left(θ+\frac{π}{4}\right)}=sin\ {\left(\frac{π}{3}\right)}⇒θ+\frac{π}{4}=\frac{π}{3}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ffa1f330-261c-477f-9bb9-2b1bf8de64d1">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ffa1f330-261c-477f-9bb9-2b1bf8de64d1 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ffa1f330-261c-477f-9bb9-2b1bf8de64d1 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000c8508f21-57af-404c-852a-237bf3f25c1a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒θ=\frac{π}{3}-\frac{π}{4}=\frac{4π-3π}{12}=\frac{π}{12}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001c8508f21-57af-404c-852a-237bf3f25c1a"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c8508f21-57af-404c-852a-237bf3f25c1a {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001c8508f21-57af-404c-852a-237bf3f25c1a {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
