                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000091ddf3a4-c430-4a47-8d67-e411eaea9dde" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(4{sec}^{2}\ {\left({tan}^{-1}\ {\frac{1}{2}}+{sec}^{-1}\ {\frac{\sqrt{10}}{3}}\right)}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000191ddf3a4-c430-4a47-8d67-e411eaea9dde"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000091ddf3a4-c430-4a47-8d67-e411eaea9dde {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000191ddf3a4-c430-4a47-8d67-e411eaea9dde {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000006391d729-bcfe-4e90-b844-1449a3a5fbcf" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=4{sec}^{2}\ {\left({tan}^{-1}\ {\frac{1}{2}}+{tan}^{-1}\ {\frac{1}{3}}\right)}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000016391d729-bcfe-4e90-b844-1449a3a5fbcf"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000006391d729-bcfe-4e90-b844-1449a3a5fbcf {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000016391d729-bcfe-4e90-b844-1449a3a5fbcf {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000007c8f2009-7a80-442b-80a4-c2607ce05579" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=4{sec}^{2}\ {\left(\frac{π}{4}\right)=4\times 2=8}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017c8f2009-7a80-442b-80a4-c2607ce05579"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000007c8f2009-7a80-442b-80a4-c2607ce05579 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000017c8f2009-7a80-442b-80a4-c2607ce05579 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal