                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000000661bbfe-3f88-4027-a26b-d55b56c758e6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000010661bbfe-3f88-4027-a26b-d55b56c758e6"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 0.9306354in;height: 0.7463506in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000661bbfe-3f88-4027-a26b-d55b56c758e6 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000010661bbfe-3f88-4027-a26b-d55b56c758e6 {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000002bd90642-5587-4641-bf9b-c1158b7511db" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{{T}_{1}}{sin⁡(90^{\circ} +B)}=\frac{{T}_{2}}{sin⁡(90^{\circ} +A)}=\frac{20}{sin90^{\circ} }\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012bd90642-5587-4641-bf9b-c1158b7511db"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000002bd90642-5587-4641-bf9b-c1158b7511db {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000012bd90642-5587-4641-bf9b-c1158b7511db {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000005bf37632-fe77-42af-bf74-f3ac654d8433" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴{T}_{1}=20cosB=20\times \frac{1.6}{2}kg-wt=16kg-wt\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000015bf37632-fe77-42af-bf74-f3ac654d8433"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000005bf37632-fe77-42af-bf74-f3ac654d8433 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000015bf37632-fe77-42af-bf74-f3ac654d8433 {font-family: ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000385d1896-c2be-448f-9639-e1f72efa152c" xm