                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000019d46445-89da-4404-b9a7-56cba7632990" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000119d46445-89da-4404-b9a7-56cba7632990"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 0.9166667in;height: 0.6258366in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000019d46445-89da-4404-b9a7-56cba7632990 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000119d46445-89da-4404-b9a7-56cba7632990 {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000461ee817-0ba5-4088-8958-fd90cc2a8b32" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001461ee817-0ba5-4088-8958-fd90cc2a8b32">wb‡Y&#169;q †KvY</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001461ee817-0ba5-4088-8958-fd90cc2a8b32"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=90^{\circ} +θ=90^{\circ} +{sin}^{-1}\ {\frac{u}{2u}}\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000461ee817-0ba5-4088-8958-fd90cc2a8b32 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001461ee817-0ba5-4088-8958-fd90cc2a8b32 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000013c08a01-f7bb-4c50-83f2-f513d5b96fa6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=90^{\circ} +{sin}^{-1}\ {\frac{1}{2}}=90^{\circ} +30^{\circ} =120^{\circ} \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000113c08a01-f7bb-4c50-83f2-f513d5b96fa6"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000013c08a01-f7bb-4c50-83f2-f513d5b96fa6 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000113c08a01-f7bb-4c50-83f2-f513d5b96fa6 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;pa